{"title":"参观邓家堡有感","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"参观邓家堡有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（西江月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日山穷沟险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄沙赤水横流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几多悲苦几多愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残壁断墙多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一战邓家堡上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈山蓄水填沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果香粮熟庆丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅地球新绣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（这是参加全国第三次水土保持会议的广东一代表写的）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分段流水作业深翻图"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}